# Enhanced Dashboard Features - Walkthrough

## Overview
Successfully implemented enhanced dashboard features for both Teacher and Student accounts, providing comprehensive views of assignments, performance metrics, and organizational hierarchy.

## Teacher Dashboard Enhancements

### Features Implemented

#### 1. Department/Batch Organization
- **Hierarchical View**: Organized assignments by Department → Batch → Assignments
- **Expandable Sections**: Click to expand/collapse departments and batches
- **Student Count**: Shows number of students in each batch

#### 2. Assignment Columns (Completed vs Pending)
- **Two-Column Layout**: 
  - **Pending Assignments**: Assignments with deadlines in the future (orange theme)
  - **Completed Assignments**: Assignments with past deadlines (green theme)
- **Visual Indicators**: Color-coded cards with distinct icons

#### 3. Submission Statistics
- **Submission Count**: Shows number of students who submitted each assignment
- **Quick View**: Eye icon links to Student Tracker for detailed submissions
- **Real-time Data**: Fetched from [submittedAssignments](file:///c:/Users/bhuva/IAFP/frontEnd/IAFP/src/services/Api.jsx#114-132) API

#### 4. Dashboard Stats
- **Active Assignments**: Total count of all assignments
- **Total Students**: Count of students across all departments/batches
- **Pending Reviews**: Number of incomplete submissions

### Technical Implementation

**File**: [TeacherHome.jsx](file:///c:/Users/bhuva/IAFP/frontEnd/IAFP/src/components/TeacherHome.jsx)

**APIs Used**:
- [fetchAssignment()](file:///c:/Users/bhuva/IAFP/frontEnd/IAFP/src/components/S_fetchAssignments.jsx#16-29) - Get all teacher's assignments
- [submittedAssignments()](file:///c:/Users/bhuva/IAFP/frontEnd/IAFP/src/services/Api.jsx#114-132) - Get all student submissions
- [students_by_department()](file:///c:/Users/bhuva/IAFP/frontEnd/IAFP/src/services/Api.jsx#95-113) - Get students grouped by department

**Key Features**:
- State management for expanded/collapsed sections
- Real-time deadline checking to categorize assignments
- Dynamic organization by department and batch
- Submission count calculation per assignment

