## Student Dashboard Enhancements

### Features Implemented

#### 1. Dashboard Metrics Cards
Four key metrics displayed prominently:
- **Pending Assignments**: Count of assignments with future deadlines
- **Available Assignments**: Total assignments count
- **Average Grade**: Calculated from published evaluations
- **Total Subjects**: Unique count of subjects

#### 2. Assignment History View
- **Recent Grades**: Last 5 graded assignments with scores
- **Feedback Preview**: AI-generated feedback snippets
- **Subject Tags**: Clear subject identification
- **Date Display**: When the grade was published

#### 3. Upcoming Deadlines
- **Priority Sorting**: Urgent assignments highlighted in red
- **Days Count**: Shows "Today", "Tomorrow", or "X days" remaining
- **Visual Indicators**: Color-coded dots (red = urgent, yellow = normal)
- **Subject Information**: Display assignment subject and title

#### 4. Available Assignments Grid
- **Card Layout**: 3-column grid showing all available assignments
- **Status Badges**: "Active" or "Due" based on deadline
- **Question Count**: Number of questions per assignment
- **Quick Links**: Click to go to full assignment view

### Technical Implementation

**File**: [StudentHomePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/bhuva/IAFP/frontEnd/IAFP/src/components/StudentHomePage.jsx)

**APIs Used**:
- [fetchAssignments()](file:///c:/Users/bhuva/IAFP/frontEnd/IAFP/src/components/A_fetchAssignments.jsx#21-29) - Get student's assignments based on department/batch
- [fetchFeedback()](file:///c:/Users/bhuva/IAFP/frontEnd/IAFP/src/services/Api.jsx#264-281) - Get student's evaluation history

**Key Features**:
- Real-time statistics calculation
- Deadline tracking with day counting
- Average grade calculation from published evaluations
- Unique subject identification
- Responsive grid layouts

