## Data Flow

### Teacher Dashboard
```
fetchAssignment() → Get all assignments by teacher
submittedAssignments() → Get all submissions
students_by_department() → Get students
↓
Organize by: Department → Year → Deadline Status
↓
Display: Expandable hierarchy with two-column assignment view
```

### Student Dashboard
```
fetchAssignments() → Get assignments for student's dept/batch
fetchFeedback() → Get evaluations
↓
Calculate: Pending count, Average grade, Unique subjects
↓
Display: Metrics cards, Upcoming deadlines, Assignment history
```

